Datascope Analytics or Datascope is a data-driven consulting and design firm based in Chicago IL.[1] The firm was founded in 2009 by co-founders Mike Stringer and Dean Malmgren after the two realized the lodes that could be extracted from data science.[2] In addition to analyzing massive amounts of data the firm builds useful tools for people organizations and companies to learn from data and be more quantitative in how they approach different problems. Their data science services include strategy consulting software development and training.
